io.micronaut.configuration.kafka.processor

Class KafkaConsumerProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.micronaut.configuration.kafka.processor.KafkaConsumerProcessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConsumerRegistry, io.micronaut.context.processor.AnnotationProcessor<KafkaListener,io.micronaut.inject.ExecutableMethod<?,?>>, io.micronaut.context.processor.ExecutableMethodProcessor<KafkaListener>, java.lang.AutoCloseable

    @Singleton
 @Requires(beans=KafkaDefaultConfiguration.class)
public class KafkaConsumerProcessor
extends java.lang.Object
implements io.micronaut.context.processor.ExecutableMethodProcessor<KafkaListener>, java.lang.AutoCloseable, ConsumerRegistry

    A ExecutableMethodProcessor that will process all beans annotated with KafkaListener and create and subscribe the relevant methods as consumers to Kafka topics.

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Graeme Rocher
